<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.6.10">
<l>kaṭikamaḻu neṭumaṟukil kaṭaṉmallait talacayaṉat</l>
<l>taṭikaḷaṭi yēniṉaiyu maṭiyavarkaḷ tammaṭiyāṉ</l>
<l>vaṭikoṇeṭu vēlvalavaṉ kalikaṉṟi yolivallār</l>
<l>muṭikoṇeṭu maṉṉavartam mutalvarmu talāvārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the words of Kaliyaṉ, the one skilled</l>
<l rend="indent">with the long, sharp spear,</l>
<l>The servant of the servants who think only of the feet of the lord</l>
<l>Of Talacayaṉam at Mallai by the sea, where fragrances waft in long streets,</l>
<l>They will become the best among the best of great, crowned kings.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
